# Professional Statement

## 👋 About Me
Hello! I am an aspiring Cybersecurity Analyst with a passion for protecting digital assets and mitigating cyber threats. I am currently completing the Google Cybersecurity Professional Certificate, where I have developed hands-on skills in security auditing, Linux administration, SQL querying, incident response, and network analysis.

